84503.notes:
Contact:
Alexandra 



The Robes come in the three sizes. 
Size 1: X-small to a Small-Medium 
Size 2: Medium-Large
Size 3: Large-Extra Large 
 
The Pajamas come in 4 sizes
Size 1: X-Small/Small
Size 2: Small/Medium
Size 3: Medium/Large
Size 4: Large/Extra Large


Tips about the items:

  • Posy garments are made from rayon which not only is lovely and soft, but it's breathable! This is super important for the big day, especially as brides will most likely already be warm. 
  • I recommend a cool iron or steam prior to wearing the garments. 
  • Garments should be washed separately in cold water. Rayon could shrink in a really hot wash!
  • I also recommend sizing up if in between sizes, or if anyone is particularly tall with the robes they should also size up for extra length. (My sister is very slim and tall and she wore the size 3 for my wedding).
  • All prints are exclusive to Posy and designed by local and international designers 
  • Depending on time frames for the brides, I can sometimes do custom orders. It would just depend on what fabric I have available at the time, but if they are ordering in advance it's possible. Same with junior's.
